<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="24Feb1928"><font color="red">24 February 1928</font> <i>BLHW</i> (to Harriet Weaver): I am still here &lsquo;moidered&rsquo; with work &hellip; I have had to take on a kind of temporary secretary, McGreevy, to help my eyelessness. Friede has made over his copyright to me by transfer deed &hellip; Lewis has been sent on a mission to India by Chatto &amp; Windus for his next &lsquo;indiapepper edition shortly&rsquo; &hellip; Thanks for <i>Blast</i>. I have to struggle through 16 notebooks for the revision of <font face="wake">D</font>a alone &hellip; I send you proofs as they grow </div>
